name: WorldofTrends
0:
”Alexa, open world of trends”
”Alexa, ask World of Trends to tell me what is trending”
”Alexa, ask World of trends who is in the top charts of Actors”
skdetail:
This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: world of trends
des:
Searching for latest trends could be so much trouble these days. So we at HAN present you the latest skill, World of Trends.
This skill will tell you about the viral trends going on around the world. Just ask Alexa "What is trending". 
Not able to remember what you were looking for, don't worry, this skill is capable of telling the topics related to your 'keyword'. 
Want to know who is the most trending actor, or which game is the most famous, worry not, because we provide top charts too. Just ask Alexa who is on the top charts of Actors or What is on the top charts of Games. The top charts is limited to some topics, but it is dynamic, so it will change with time. You can ask Alexa to tell you the topics which it supports.
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
